@model aspPro2.Models.Games
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutGame";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_NewLayout1.cshtml";
}
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/AboutGame.css" />

</head>

<section>
    <h1 id="text">Mage's Survival: Monster Wilds</h1>
    <img src="~/images/cover.jpg" alt="Alternate Text" />
    <a class="btn">download Game</a>
</section>
<div class="Story">
    <h2>about game story</h2>

    <p id="p1">
        A once-thriving magical kingdom, now overrun by monstrous creatures and dark magic.
        The kingdom is set in a sprawling, enchanted 
        forest teeming with mystical flora and fauna, ancient ruins, and hidden dangers.
    </p>
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img1" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p2">
        Prologue: The kingdom of Eldoria was a land of magic and wonder,
        where mages and magical creatures coexisted in harmony. However, 
        an ancient and malevolent force, long sealed away by the kingdom's most powerful mages, 
        has been accidentally unleashed. This dark entity, known as the Void Wraith, has corrupted the land, 
        causing monstrous creatures to emerge and the once-pure magic to turn malevolent.
    </p>
   @*  <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img2" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p3">
        Introduction: You are a young and talented mage, recently graduated from the Arcane Academy. 
        As the kingdom’s last hope, you are thrust into a world of chaos and darkness. Your mentor, the head mage, 
        has vanished in the midst of the crisis, and it's up to you to restore balance and save Eldoria.
    </p >
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img3" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id ="p4">
        Act 1 - The Corrupted Wilds: You begin your journey in the outskirts of Eldoria, 
        where the forest is overrun by twisted creatures. Your initial goal is to gather 
        information about the Void Wraith and the source of its power. You encounter survivors
        and magical beings who provide clues and aid in your quest. 
        Your battles with corrupted monsters help you learn and harness new spells and abilities.
    </p >
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img4" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p5">
        Act 2 - The Forgotten Ruins: As you venture deeper,
        you discover ancient ruins that hold secrets about the Void Wraith's origins 
        and the spells used to imprison it. These ruins are guarded by powerful monsters 
        and ancient traps. Solving puzzles and overcoming challenges in these ruins reveals 
        that the Void Wraith's influence is spreading, 
        and only a powerful relic, hidden in the heart of the forest, can stop it.
    </p>
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img5" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p6">
        Act 3 - The Heart of Darkness: The final stage of your journey takes you to the core of 
        the corruption—the Dark Citadel, where the Void Wraith resides. The citadel is a labyrinth 
        of danger, filled with the strongest and most grotesque creatures. You must navigate through 
        treacherous traps and powerful enemies while gathering the relic's
        pieces needed to seal the Void Wraith once again.
    </p>
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img6" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p7">
        Climax: Confront the Void Wraith in an epic battle. Use your knowledge, 
        skills, and the relic to defeat the Wraith and restore the kingdom's magic. 
        The battle will test everything you’ve 
        learned and require strategic use of your spells and items.
    </p>
    @* <img src="~/images/sa7r2.png" id="img7" /> *@
    <br />
    <p id="p8">
        Resolution: With the Void Wraith defeated and the corruption lifted, Eldoria begins to heal. 
        The magical creatures and survivors return to their peaceful lives. You are celebrated as a 
        hero and become a revered mage in the kingdom, with a new understanding of the delicate 
        balance between magic and the natural world.
    </p>

	
</div>